# ─── VA3YMX Caddy (HTTPS reverse proxy) — environment TEMPLATE ───────────────
# Copy to ".env" and fill in.  The real .env holds the secret and is .gitignore'd.

# DreamHost API key with "All DNS functions" permission — used by the
# caddy-dns/dreamhost plugin for the Let's Encrypt DNS-01 wildcard challenge.
# Create one at:  https://panel.dreamhost.com/?tree=home.api
DREAMHOST_API_KEY=PUT-YOUR-DREAMHOST-API-KEY-HERE
